<!-- Quiz Content -->
<main class="w3-content" style="max-width:900px; margin-top:30px;">


<div class="card w3-card w3-padding w3-white">


<p>
Test your knowledge of the Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP).
Complete all questions and submit your answers to see your score.
</p>



<form id="quizForm">



<!-- Question 1 -->

<h3>Question 1: Fill in the Blank</h3>

<p>
HTTP stands for __________ Transfer Protocol.
</p>


<input 
type="text"
id="q1"
class="w3-input w3-border"
placeholder="Enter your answer">



<hr>



<!-- Question 2 -->

<h3>Question 2: Multiple Choice</h3>

<p>
Who invented HTTP?
</p>


<input type="radio" name="q2" value="A">
Bill Gates
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q2" value="B">
Tim Berners-Lee
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q2" value="C">
Steve Jobs
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q2" value="D">
Mark Zuckerberg



<hr>




<!-- Question 3 -->

<h3>Question 3: Multiple Choice</h3>

<p>
Which HTTP version introduced multiplexing?
</p>


<input type="radio" name="q3" value="A">
HTTP/1.0
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q3" value="B">
HTTP/1.1
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q3" value="C">
HTTP/2
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q3" value="D">
FTP



<hr>




<!-- Question 4 -->

<h3>Question 4: Multiple Choice</h3>

<p>
Which protocol does HTTP/3 use?
</p>


<input type="radio" name="q4" value="A">
TCP
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q4" value="B">
FTP
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q4" value="C">
SMTP
<br>


<input type="radio" name="q4" value="D">
QUIC



<hr>





<!-- Question 5 -->

<h3>Question 5: Select All Correct Answers</h3>


<p>
Which are features of HTTP/2?
</p>



<input type="checkbox" id="q5a">
Multiplexing

<br>


<input type="checkbox" id="q5b">
Header Compression

<br>


<input type="checkbox" id="q5c">
FTP Support

<br>


<input type="checkbox" id="q5d">
Built on QUIC



<hr>





